      "authorImage": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_msY3C36bIC4p_HINPjegiOcplRhtVYXi0UeIrwc3o=s48-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj",
      "text": "2",
      "likeCount": 1,
      "publishedAt": "2026-07-11T01:40:37Z",
      "replyCount": 1,
      "replies": [
        {
          "id": "UgxNOi7QQLa8-NnlcKt4AaABAg.AZ66mW5byGXAZ6I0WJJZ0j",
          "author": "@MundoDescifrado.001",
          "authorImage": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/2ClRV2wxM2cwbUDsPtBKGjHdVgSqnjUFMJ9BBHOGAg8IMyTGgoY9RkJz7FLmF3indjQjkOqKJg=s48-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj",
          "text": "Las encantadoras mujeres de aquí respetan a un hombre de acción. Preséntate con caballerosidad, demuestra que tienes la estabilidad para proteger y reserva ese vuelo de inmediato.",
          "likeCount": 0,
          "publishedAt": "2026-07-11T03:18:46Z"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "UgwmKjz6oTg2zoZwPZh4AaABAg",
      "author": "@MrCapa2211",
      "authorImage": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_lf_kurAfqwqrDqct_0Hu5QOTT5aOpbqpjQBlBtWhg=s48-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj",
      "text": "2",
      "likeCount": 1,
      "publishedAt": "2026-07-11T02:40:13Z",
      "replyCount": 1,
      "replies": [
        {
          "id": "UgwmKjz6oTg2zoZwPZh4AaABAg.AZ6Db9CAJNhAZ6I1iCdW6l",
          "author": "@MundoDescifrado.001",
          "authorImage": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/2ClRV2wxM2cwbUDsPtBKGjHdVgSqnjUFMJ9BBHOGAg8IMyTGgoY9RkJz7FLmF3indjQjkOqKJg=s48-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj",
          "text": "Deja de pensar demasiado desde el sofá de tu casa. Un hombre estable con intenciones sinceras y un vuelo reservado es exactamente lo que ellas están buscando. Es hora de hacer las maletas y ponerse en camino.",
          "likeCount": 0,
          "publishedAt": "2026-07-11T03:18:56Z"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Ugw7aUUzpGvWPEiJo8B4AaABAg",
      "author": "@cruzperez5127",
      "authorImage": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_n3m7xeWn5ptA_zwpmU81y3O6-jbv8WvjnnpyQKbi9YeNOmEZNThwjQW3EwN3-DVI6pDA=s48-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj",
      "text": "2",
      "likeCount": 1,
      "publishedAt": "2026-07-11T04:37:34Z",
      "replyCount": 1,
      "replies": [
        {
          "id": "Ugw7aUUzpGvWPEiJo8B4AaABAg.AZ6R1c_YvuZAZ6TNnSsqs7",
          "author": "@MundoDescifrado.001",
          "authorImage": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/2ClRV2wxM2cwbUDsPtBKGjHdVgSqnjUFMJ9BBHOGAg8IMyTGgoY9RkJz7FLmF3indjQjkOqKJg=s48-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj",
          "text": "Las mujeres de calidad siempre buscan hombres con una vida sólida y autónoma. Preséntate con elegancia, una capacidad financiera clara e introduce tu persona directamente cara a cara.",
          "likeCount": 0,
